notes: Bishen Bedi conceded the match in protest against the short pitched bowling tactics of Pakistan. Sarfraz Nawaz's last 4 deliveries were all out of reach of the batsmen, and not called wide by the umpire.

milestones.description: Amarnath has become the top wicket-taker for IND in ODIs with 9 wickets, going past Bishan Bedi's 7
Bishan Bedi has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for IND, going past Srinivas Venkataraghavan's 3
Srinivas Venkataraghavan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for IND, going past Viswanath
This is the highest match aggregate (388) involving teams India & Pakistan in ODIs
Pakistan's 23-run win against India is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 36-run win against England
Gaekwad and Amarnath's 119-run partnership is IND's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 53 between Gaekwad and Amarnath
